{
  "text": "iTRAQ-based LC-MS analysis of protein expression profile of ER/microsomal vesicles-enriched fraction of cells with or without celastrol treatment. The ER/microsomal vesicles-enriched fraction of cells with or without celastrol treatment (1 mM celastrol for 48 h) were prepared similar to previous report. [CITATION_1] Detailed information can be found in Supplementary Materials and Methods.",
